# Cloudflare Pages headers (funnel — taimotion.com)
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
# Security headers apply to every response. Caching is left to Cloudflare's
# defaults (HTML served fresh, static assets cached); asset cache-busting keeps
# relying on the ?v=NN query strings in the HTML.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()

# Keep guide PDFs and the internal/demo pages out of search engines
# (the public marketing pages — home, quiz — stay indexable).
